{"tid":1247592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【民建聯就蔣麗芸議員言論的回應】","createTime":"2019-06-21T07:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T03:09:44.000Z","uid":11512,"like":412,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"0e22e148907645504d13615925cd6d094ae0748b","tid":1247592,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"就蔣麗芸議員今日接受訪問時，表示在政府加強宣傳後，屆時政府可衡量是否重推逃犯條例修訂。蔣麗芸亦表明今早言論，只屬個人意見，並沒有在黨內討論。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯理解和尊重特首作出暫緩修例的決定，以避免社會進一步撕裂，讓社會回復平靜。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於社會對修例意見分歧，我們認同政府未就重啟修例定下時間表的做法，並認為只有在公眾充份了解，並取得共識後，才考慮下一階段工作。"},{"pid":"e07133465273b63007298aa141cffebe97b45104","tid":1247592,"uid":11512,"like":384,"dislike":0,"score":384,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<br />\n自己同自己割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2004d622cc329587f903ffadfc5a296715f1df57","tid":1247592,"uid":49336,"like":121,"dislike":2,"score":119,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"公開割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2b20d50a152e98b9bc268cb411b4e18c5a3cd7","tid":1247592,"uid":153600,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"下屆垃圾會唔知仲有冇人投佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a56306db6e45be7d8a0c0d5ac241aea47c4e86","tid":1247592,"uid":11512,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"source : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/dab.hk.1992/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fdab.hk.1992%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=d67eb7b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/dab.hk